stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Scan: cron / admin trigger

    Scan --> SuggestionCreated: nano swarm detects inconsistency
    Scan --> Scan: no issues found (continue)

    SuggestionCreated --> Deduplicated: dedup + rate-limit check
    Deduplicated --> Pending: persisted to Redis

    Pending --> UnderReview: reviewer opens suggestion

    UnderReview --> Accepted: reviewer accepts
    UnderReview --> Rejected: reviewer rejects
    UnderReview --> Edited: reviewer edits resolution

    Edited --> Accepted: confirm edit

    Accepted --> Resolving: claim Redis lock<br/>reload + preflight
    Resolving --> Resolved: success / partial
    Resolving --> Pending: failed is retryable
    Rejected --> Dismissed: logged + feedback captured

    Resolved --> FeedbackLoop: feedback available to future audits
    Dismissed --> FeedbackLoop: rationale available to future audits

    FeedbackLoop --> [*]: review data stored

    note right of Pending
        Suggestions are deduped in Redis
        before reaching the reviewer.
        No duplicate noise.
    end note

    note right of Resolved
        App handlers/adapters own durable
        effects. Current SSA promotion
        appends sweep_audit; confidence
        promotion is still placeholder.
    end note
